profile: My name is Timothy Toner, I graduated from NBCC Woodstock from the carpentry program in 2008.  From then I worked in the industry building and installing countertops and in 2014 I decided to open up my own business.  We are a small family business specializing in Corian solid surface countertops.  We also offer excellent quality quartz, granite, and butcher block countertops.  We can provide you with the entire kitchen countertop replacement renovation experience.  From removing the existing surfaces and installing new quality-made countertops with sink and faucet and new tile backsplash.
